  EffectDiscription_ENG: "When you would play this card from the hand, if you have
    no Digimon, reduce the play cost by 2 for every 5 total cards in both players'
    trashes.\uFF1CRush\uFF1E (This Digimon can attack the turn it was played.) [On
    Play][When Digivolving][When Attacking] Delete 1 of your opponent's Digimon with
    6000 DP or less. If no opponent's Digimon was deleted by this effect, delete
    1 of their Digimon with 13000 DP or more."
